  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">HELP US EDUCATE CHILDREN IN RURAL INDIA</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sampa is fifteen and a first generation learner. She lives with her family in a bamboo house with no electricity and no running water. Her father is a labourer and her mother cuts grass, bringing in an income of 500 per year. Since starting our education classes, Sampa&apos;s become ambitious and wants to be a teacher!  We are so happy to be there for her, but 8 million children drop out of school at ten years old in India. We want this to stop. We want to reach many more children like Sampa.</narrative>
  </description>
